Broccoli and Stilton Soup for 3

Simple and tasty variation of the classic.

1 tablespoon oil
1 onion, diced
1 broccoli, chopped
1 large potato, cubed
800ml chicken stock
70g stilton, chopped

blend(
	stir in(
		simmer 20 min(
		cook until veg releases moisture(
			cook slowly until translucent(oil, onion),
			broccoli,
			large potato),
		chicken stock),
		stilton))
